論文著作與研究計畫

TING, H. Y. (2013) Fostering Creative Pedagogy among Secondary Art Teacher Training Students in Taiwan: Investigating the Introduction of Possibility Thinking as a Core of Creative Pedagogy in a Workshop Intervention. PhD thesis in Education, University of Exeter, UK.(培育台灣中等美術師資培育學生之創意力教學法：以可能性思考為核心的創造力教學工作坊為初探)
TING, H. Y. (2008) The conceptions of Creative Pedagogy among Secondary Art Teacher Training Students in Taiwan: A Case Study. MSc dissertation in Educational Research, University of Exeter, UK.(個案研究：台灣中等視覺藝術師資培育學生之創意教學的概念認知)
TING, H. Y. (2007) The Comparative Study: Initial Art Teacher Education in secondary schools between England and Taiwan. MEd dissertation in Visual Art and the Creative Arts in Education, University of Exeter, UK.(台灣與英國中等教育階段視覺藝術師資培育制度之比較研究)



